msgid ""
"Troubleshoot Klein for Ray installation, execution-mode, connector, "
"checkpoint, watermark, backpressure, and CLI problems."
msgstr "排查 Klein for Ray 的安装、执行模式、连接器、检查点、水位线、背压和 CLI 问题。"

msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "故障排查"

msgid ""
"Start by saving the job plan, namespace, effective explicit "
"configuration, Klein/Ray versions, first exception, and recent checkpoint"
" history. Later actor failures are often consequences of the first error."
msgstr ""
"首先保存作业计划、命名空间、生效的显式配置、Klein/Ray 版本、首个异常和最近的检查点历史。后续 actor "
"故障通常是第一个错误所导致的结果。"

msgid ""
"Never paste credentials, complete connector configuration, arbitrary "
"records, or checkpoint payloads into an issue or log bundle."
msgstr "切勿将凭据、完整连接器配置、任意记录或检查点载荷粘贴到 issue 或日志包中。"

msgid "Installation and imports"
msgstr "安装与导入"

msgid "`ModuleNotFoundError` for a connector dependency"
msgstr "连接器依赖引发 `ModuleNotFoundError`"

msgid ""
"Install the matching extra on every worker image, not only on the "
"submitting machine:"
msgstr "请在每个 worker 镜像上安装相应的 extra，而不只是在提交作业的机器上安装："

msgid ""
"RocketMQ additionally needs a compatible native `librocketmq`. A Python "
"wheel being importable on the driver does not prove the native library "
"exists on a remote worker."
msgstr ""
"RocketMQ 还需要兼容的原生 `librocketmq`。driver 能够导入 Python wheel，并不能证明远程 worker "
"上存在该原生库。"

msgid "Dynamic `read_*` or `stream.data` method is unavailable"
msgstr "动态 `read_*` 或 `stream.data` 方法不可用"

msgid "Check the installed Ray API before building the graph:"
msgstr "构建图之前，请检查已安装的 Ray API："

msgid ""
"Klein discovers public Ray Data factories and Dataset methods at runtime."
" Stay inside the Ray range in [Compatibility](compatibility.md)."
msgstr ""
"Klein 在运行时发现公共 Ray Data 工厂和 Dataset 方法。请使用[兼容性](compatibility.md)中规定的 Ray"
" 版本范围。"

msgid "Planning and execution mode"
msgstr "规划与执行模式"

msgid "`Batch function is not defined`"
msgstr "`Batch function is not defined`"

msgid ""
"The graph selected batch execution but contains a native-streaming-only "
"source, operator, or sink. Check [Operator compatibility](operator-"
"compatibility.md). Set `execution.runtime.mode=streaming` only when every"
" node supports native streaming; changing the mode cannot give a Ray "
"Data-only operation a streaming implementation."
msgstr ""
"图选择了批执行，但包含仅支持原生流处理的源、算子或 sink。请检查[算子兼容性](operator-"
"compatibility.md)。只有每个节点都支持原生流处理时，才设置 "
"`execution.runtime.mode=streaming`；更改模式无法为仅支持 Ray Data 的操作提供流式实现。"

msgid "A bounded custom source does not run in batch"
msgstr "有界自定义数据源未以批处理模式运行"

msgid ""
"Source boundedness does not prove that a custom `SourceFunction` has a "
"Ray Data lowering. `auto` selects streaming when that lowering is absent."
" Use a Ray Data factory or `from_ray_dataset()` when batch execution is "
"required; forcing `batch` cannot add a missing lowering."
msgstr ""
"数据源有界并不能证明自定义 `SourceFunction` 具有 Ray Data 下沉实现。缺少该下沉实现时，`auto` 会选择流处理。"
"需要批处理执行时，请使用 Ray Data 工厂或 `from_ray_dataset()`；强制使用 `batch` 无法补上缺失的下沉实现。"

msgid "Streams from different pipelines cannot be combined"
msgstr "无法组合来自不同管道的流"

msgid ""
"Every graph belongs to one internal pipeline. Rebuild all branches from "
"the same module-level construction scope; do not join or union those "
"streams with streams built by an explicitly isolated advanced context."
msgstr "每个图都属于一个内部管道。请在同一模块级构建作用域中重新构建所有分支；不要将这些流与显式隔离的高级上下文所构建的流进行 join 或 union。"

msgid "SQL fails during planning"
msgstr "SQL 在规划期间失败"

msgid ""
"Confirm whether the selected mode supports the statement. Continuous SQL "
"supports a smaller subset than batch SQL and deliberately rejects "
"unsupported CTEs, outer joins, arbitrary ordering, window syntax, and "
"other forms rather than changing semantics. Check table changelog "
"compatibility before attaching a sink."
msgstr ""
"请确认所选模式是否支持该语句。持续 SQL 支持的子集小于批处理 SQL，并会有意拒绝不受支持的 "
"CTE、外连接、任意排序、窗口语法及其他形式，而不是更改语义。挂接 sink 前，请检查表变更日志兼容性。"

msgid "Jobs and CLI"
msgstr "作业与 CLI"

msgid "`ray-klein list` cannot query the Ray state API"
msgstr "`ray-klein list` 无法查询 Ray 状态 API"

msgid ""
"Confirm that the client can reach the Ray cluster, the dashboard/state "
"service is enabled, and `ray.init(address=\"auto\")` would attach to the "
"intended cluster. Network policy must allow the client to reach the "
"cluster control plane."
msgstr ""
"请确认客户端能够访问 Ray 集群、dashboard/state 服务已启用，且 `ray.init(address=\"auto\")` "
"会附加到预期集群。网络策略必须允许客户端访问集群控制平面。"

msgid "`No JobManager found in namespace ...`"
msgstr "`No JobManager found in namespace ...`"

msgid ""
"Use `ray-klein list` to copy the exact namespace. An automatically "
"generated namespace includes a sanitized job name and an eight-character "
"suffix. A job ID from the state snapshot API is not interchangeable with "
"every CLI argument."
msgstr ""
"使用 `ray-klein list` 复制准确的命名空间。自动生成的命名空间包含清理后的作业名称和八字符后缀。状态快照 API 中的作业 ID "
"不能与每个 CLI 参数互换使用。"

msgid "`attach` says stdout is not a TTY"
msgstr "`attach` 提示 stdout 不是 TTY"

msgid ""
"Live progress rendering requires an interactive terminal. Use `status` or"
" the JSON-safe state API from automation."
msgstr "实时进度渲染需要交互式终端。自动化程序应使用 `status` 或可安全序列化为 JSON 的状态 API。"

msgid "Ctrl+C did not stop the job"
msgstr "Ctrl+C 未停止作业"

msgid ""
"Ctrl+C while attached detaches intentionally. Run `ray-klein stop "
"<namespace>` or call `JobHandle.cancel()` to cancel the detached job."
msgstr ""
"附加状态下按 Ctrl+C 会按设计解除附加。运行 `ray-klein stop <namespace>` 或调用 "
"`JobHandle.cancel()` 取消 detached 作业。"

msgid "Checkpoints and recovery"
msgstr "检查点与恢复"

msgid "No completed checkpoint appears"
msgstr "没有出现已完成的检查点"

msgid ""
"Check that at least one trigger is enabled, sources are still emitting "
"idle or checkpoint control, all sinks acknowledge barriers, and storage "
"is writable. Setting both trigger intervals to zero disables periodic "
"barriers. A blocked source that never calls `on_idle()` can also delay "
"time-based progress."
msgstr ""
"请检查是否至少启用了一个触发器、源是否仍在发出空闲或检查点控制消息、所有 sink "
"是否确认屏障，以及存储是否可写。将两个触发间隔都设为零会禁用周期性屏障。从不调用 `on_idle()` 的阻塞源也会延迟基于时间的进度。"

msgid "Restore silently starts from the beginning"
msgstr "恢复静默地从头开始"

msgid ""
"Use the exact key `execution.savepoint.path` and pass the full completed "
"`chk-N` URI. Unknown configuration keys are retained, so a misspelled "
"restore key does not necessarily raise an error."
msgstr ""
"请使用准确的键 `execution.savepoint.path`，并传入完整的已完成 `chk-N` "
"URI。未知配置键会被保留，因此恢复键拼写错误不一定会引发错误。"

msgid "Restore reports checksum or metadata errors"
msgstr "恢复报告校验和或元数据错误"

msgid ""
"Do not edit `_metadata` or serialized state. Verify storage consistency "
"and permissions, then try an earlier retained checkpoint. An unsupported "
"format version requires the matching Klein release or an explicit "
"migration."
msgstr ""
"不要编辑 `_metadata` 或序列化状态。请验证存储一致性和权限，然后尝试更早保留的检查点。不受支持的格式版本需要匹配的 Klein "
"发行版或显式迁移。"

msgid "Restore fails after changing concurrency"
msgstr "更改并发后恢复失败"

msgid ""
"Keep `state.keyed.max-parallelism`, operator identity, state descriptor "
"names, and serializers stable. New concurrency must not exceed max "
"parallelism. See [Restore and rescale](checkpoint-recovery.md)."
msgstr ""
"请保持 `state.keyed.max-parallelism`、算子身份、状态描述符名称和 serializer "
"稳定。新并发不得超过最大并行度。请参阅[恢复与扩缩容](checkpoint-recovery.md)。"

msgid "Event time and state"
msgstr "事件时间与状态"

msgid "Windows never emit"
msgstr "窗口始终不发出结果"

msgid "Verify all of the following:"
msgstr "请验证以下所有条件："

msgid "timestamps are non-negative integer milliseconds;"
msgstr "时间戳是非负整数毫秒值；"

msgid "a watermark strategy or source emits watermarks;"
msgstr "水位线策略或源会发出水位线；"

msgid "every active physical input has emitted its first watermark;"
msgstr "每个活动物理输入都已发出其第一个水位线；"

msgid "empty inputs are marked idle;"
msgstr "空输入已标记为空闲；"

msgid "the watermark has passed the window end plus allowed lateness."
msgstr "水位线已经越过窗口结束时间与允许延迟之和。"

msgid "Records carrying timestamps do not advance event time by themselves."
msgstr "携带时间戳的记录本身不会推进事件时间。"

msgid "`late_records_dropped` rises"
msgstr "`late_records_dropped` 上升"

msgid ""
"Compare record timestamps with the current input/output watermark and "
"`allowed_lateness`. Look for clock/unit mistakes—seconds interpreted as "
"milliseconds are common—and for partitions reactivating with old data. "
"Raising allowed lateness retains more state and delays window cleanup."
msgstr ""
"将记录时间戳与当前输入/输出水位线及 `allowed_lateness` "
"进行比较。检查时钟/单位错误——将秒误作毫秒很常见——以及分区是否携带旧数据重新激活。提高允许延迟会保留更多状态，并延后窗口清理。"

msgid "Managed state grows without bound"
msgstr "托管状态无限增长"

msgid ""
"Confirm that the key cardinality is expected, add descriptor TTL or an "
"operator `state_ttl` where semantics allow, and verify watermark progress"
" for event-time-cleaned state. TTL is a correctness choice: expiration "
"can make late future results incomplete."
msgstr ""
"请确认键基数符合预期；在语义允许时添加描述符 TTL 或算子 `state_ttl`；对于由事件时间清理的状态，还要验证水位线进度。TTL "
"是正确性选择：过期可能使未来的迟到结果不完整。"

msgid "Backpressure and memory"
msgstr "背压与内存"

msgid "Throughput falls while input buffers stay full"
msgstr "输入缓冲区持续满载时吞吐量下降"

msgid ""
"Find the first downstream operator with rising processing latency or "
"external call duration. Increase capacity there or reduce its work before"
" enlarging upstream buffers. Check hot keys, sink throttling, and "
"checkpoint alignment."
msgstr "找到第一个处理延迟或外部调用持续时间上升的下游算子。增大上游缓冲区之前，应提高该处容量或减少其工作量。检查热点键、sink 限流和检查点对齐。"

msgid "Replay buffer exceeds its byte limit"
msgstr "重放缓冲区超过字节限制"

msgid ""
"This is a safety failure, not a request to raise the limit automatically."
" Inspect downstream acknowledgements, checkpoint/sink completion, network"
" errors, and task restarts. Raise the limit only after measuring worst-"
"case memory on the same node shape."
msgstr ""
"这是安全保护失败，不表示应自动提高限制。请检查下游确认、检查点/sink "
"完成情况、网络错误和任务重启。只有在相同节点规格上测量最坏情况内存后，才提高限制。"

msgid "Placement group times out"
msgstr "Placement group 超时"

msgid ""
"Compare the plan's total CPU/GPU bundles with currently free cluster "
"resources. Add capacity, reduce requests, change the placement strategy, "
"or use balanced deployment. Klein may fall back to another placement "
"path, but locality and startup time can change."
msgstr ""
"将计划的 CPU/GPU bundle 总量与当前空闲集群资源进行比较。增加容量、减少请求、更改放置策略，或使用 balanced "
"deployment。Klein 可能回退到其他放置路径，但局部性和启动时间可能发生变化。"

msgid "Collect a useful report"
msgstr "收集有用的报告"

msgid "Include:"
msgstr "请包含："

msgid "minimal graph code and whether the source is bounded;"
msgstr "最小图代码以及源是否有界；"

msgid "`ray.klein.explain()` output;"
msgstr "`ray.klein.explain()` 输出；"

msgid "Klein, Ray, Python, operating system, and connector versions;"
msgstr "Klein、Ray、Python、操作系统和连接器版本；"

msgid "sanitized explicit configuration;"
msgstr "经过脱敏的显式配置；"

msgid "namespace and job status transitions;"
msgstr "命名空间和作业状态转换；"

msgid "first traceback and relevant component logs;"
msgstr "首个 traceback 和相关组件日志；"

msgid "checkpoint revision/path shape without credentials;"
msgstr "不含凭据的检查点修订版/路径形态；"

msgid "a small metric window covering the failure."
msgstr "覆盖故障时段的一小段指标窗口。"

msgid ""
"Use the repository's [support policy](https://github.com/yuchen-"
"ecnu/klein/blob/main/SUPPORT.md) for help channels and [security "
"policy](https://github.com/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/SECURITY.md) for "
"vulnerabilities or reports containing sensitive infrastructure details."
msgstr ""
"有关求助渠道，请参阅仓库的[支持策略](https://github.com/yuchen-"
"ecnu/klein/blob/main/SUPPORT.md)；有关漏洞或包含敏感基础设施详情的报告，请参阅[安全策略](https://github.com"
"/yuchen-ecnu/klein/blob/main/SECURITY.md)。"
